# Expo app (artifacts/skillsnap) — copy to `.env` if you need overrides.
#
# Do not set CI=1 when running `pnpm dev` — Expo hides the QR code in CI mode.
#
# Optional: auto-open the QR page in the default browser (writes .expo/expo-go-qr.html).
# EXPO_OPEN_QR_BROWSER=1
#
# In dev, lib/apiBase.ts prefers the Metro packager host (same Wi‑Fi as your phone) over EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL,
# so a stale IP in .env cannot break login. Use EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL for tunnels, CI, or when Metro host is wrong.

# Full API base (must include /api), e.g.:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.10:8080/api

# Android emulator → host machine API:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:8080/api

# iOS simulator / same machine:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080/api

# Optional: host-only domain for builds (see app.config.js / build scripts)
# EXPO_PUBLIC_DOMAIN=
